('http://ct-pass.com/store/show/106?lang=zh_TW', 'ChIJW1mYaoUaaTQRcS3MOL2DSEI', 0, '木匠兄妹木工坊', '為了不讓父親的木工廠因時代潮流倒閉，來自臺灣台中的一對兄妹，傳承了三代細木作工藝，加入設計 童趣、好玩的元素，發展出一系列木製家飾、文具、生活用品、玩具、童玩並開發多種親子、成人木工課程，讓樸實的木頭素材更貼近你我生活！  In Taichung,Taiwan, a brother and a sister inherit their father’s joinery techniques to preserve the family wood factory in the trend of social change in modernized society. By adding designs, children’s taste, and playful elements to the wood industry, they have not only created a series of wooden furniture, stationery, household items, and toys. The Carpenters have moreover developed various parent-child and adult courses on woodworking. Let the simple wood material get close to our lives', '台中市', 24.291618, 120.722160, NULL, '台中市后里區舊圳路4-12號', '04-2559-0689', 'https://www.facebook.com/carpenter2005/', 'https://maps.google.com.tw/maps?f=q&hl=zh-TW&geocode=&q=台中市后里區舊圳路4-12號&z=16&output=embed', '', '提供免費wifi,洗手間和旅遊諮詢,優惠套票', 'http://ct-pass.com/fileHandler/show/311', NULL, NULL, '2017-07-12 23:29:01'),
('http://ct-pass.com/store/show/107?lang=en_US', 'ChIJF2vqTGcXaTQRWs3nmvLdXvI', 1, 'Okuma Fishing Museum (寶熊漁樂館)', 'Okuma fishing was estambilished in 1986. In early days, Okuma was branding well, and distributed to Taiwan, China, USA and Europe, etc.. There are more than 60 countries use Okuma fishing products. Okuma fishing dedicated to create a fun fishig leisure, and promote the concept of fishing properly, environment protection, and cherishing marine resourse. It became the first fishing tourism factory both in Taiwan and Asia. ※Show Central Taiwan Pass, entrance ticket discount price NTD 150.', 'Taichung City', 24.220835, 120.706154, NULL, 'No.11, Sec. 3, Zhongshan Rd., Tanzi Dist., Taichung City 427, Taiwan (R.O.C.)', '886+435013338', NULL, 'https://maps.google.com.tw/maps?f=q&hl=zh-TW&geocode=&q=No.11, Sec. 3, Zhongshan Rd., Tanzi Dist., Taichung City 427, Taiwan (R.O.C.)&z=16&output=embed', 'Tuesday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Wednesday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Thursday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Friday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Saturday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Sun.,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n		\r\n			National Holiday,\r\n		\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n		\r\n			 09:30 AM~05:00 PM', 'Showing CT-PASS & get discount ticket ($150)', 'http://ct-pass.com/fileHandler/show/4188', NULL, NULL, '2017-07-12 22:44:20'),
('http://ct-pass.com/store/show/107?lang=ja', 'ChIJ29RkEbEC1zURqyBnpf7Zamw', 2, '寶熊漁樂館(寶熊漁樂館)', '寶熊漁は1986年に成立、初期はOKUMAというブランドで経営し始め、台湾本土、中国、アメリカにヨーロッパへと企業が進出し、今では60か国以上でOKUMAの商品が使われています。寶熊漁具は、生活の中の趣味として釣りというレジャーを確立し、釣りというイベントを推進し、海洋資源の環境保護にも力を入れ、2013年に観光工場補導という評価をもらい、「寶熊漁樂館」というなまえで、台湾で初の、アジア圏でも初の釣道具観光工場となりました。※台湾中部パスカード提示につき入場料が150元になります。', '河南省', 34.267494, 113.565002, NULL, '無', '無', NULL, 'https://maps.google.com.tw/maps?f=q&hl=zh-TW&geocode=&q=無&z=16&output=embed', 'Tuesday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Wednesday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Thursday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Friday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Saturday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Sun.,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n		\r\n			National Holiday,\r\n		\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n		\r\n			 09:30 AM~05:00 PM', NULL, 'http://ct-pass.com/fileHandler/show/4188', NULL, NULL, '2017-07-12 22:59:50'),
('http://ct-pass.com/store/show/107?lang=ko', 'ChIJfakwOFmpQjQRhjGTQMJaudM', 3, '보웅낚시오락관(寶熊漁樂館)', '보웅어구는 1989년에 창립되었으며 초기에는 okuma라는 브랜드로 영업을 시작하였다. 지점은 대만, 중국, 미국과 유럽등에 분포되어 있으며 전세계 60개국의 국가에서 okuma의 상품을 사용하고 있습니다. 보웅어구는 전력을 다해 낚시여가활동의 재미를 강조했으며, 환경보호와 해양자원보호와 연관된 낚시활동의 정확한개념을 알려나갔다. 2013년 관광공장으로 모습을 바꾼후, 대만의 첫번째인 동시에 아시아에서 첫번째인 낚시도구관광공장이 되었으며, 이름을 보웅낚시오락관이라 하게되었다. 타이중 하오완카드 소지시 특가표 150NT', 'Taipei City', 25.061010, 121.532852, NULL, '無', '無', NULL, 'https://maps.google.com.tw/maps?f=q&hl=zh-TW&geocode=&q=無&z=16&output=embed', 'Tuesday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Wednesday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Thursday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Friday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Saturday,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				Sun.,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n		\r\n			National Holiday,\r\n		\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n		\r\n			 09:30 AM~05:00 PM', NULL, 'http://ct-pass.com/fileHandler/show/4188', NULL, NULL, '2017-07-12 23:14:22'),
('http://ct-pass.com/store/show/107?lang=zh_TW', 'ChIJF2vqTGcXaTQRWs3nmvLdXvI', 0, '寶熊漁樂館', '寶熊漁具成立於1986年，初期即以okuma這個品牌經營，企業分布於台灣、大陸、美國與歐洲、全球超過60個國家都在使用okuma的產品。寶熊漁具，致力創造釣魚休閒生活的樂趣，以推動釣魚活動的正確觀念，提倡保護環境與海洋資源的目的。去年更配合經濟部工業局推動地方型群聚產業發展計畫，通過2013年觀光工廠輔導評鑑，成為台灣第一家、也是亞洲第一家的釣具觀光工廠，並將她命名「寶熊漁樂館」。 ※出示中台灣好玩卡，享優惠票價150元', '台中市', 24.220835, 120.706154, NULL, '台中市潭子區中山路三段11號', '04-35013338', 'http://www.okumamuseum.com.tw/', 'https://maps.google.com.tw/maps?f=q&hl=zh-TW&geocode=&q=台中市潭子區中山路三段11號&z=16&output=embed', '二,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				三,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				四,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				五,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				六,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				日,\r\n			\r\n			\r\n		\r\n			國定假日,\r\n		\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n		\r\n			 09:30 AM~05:00 PM', '出示中台灣好玩卡，憑卡購票可享優惠票價150元', 'http://ct-pass.com/fileHandler/show/4188', 'http://ct-pass.com/fileHandler/show/2540', 'http://ct-pass.com/fileHandler/show/2541', '2017-07-12 23:29:04'),
